&lt;p&gt;What if you set the $QPID_SAMPLE environment variable. AFAIU, the script expects that. The default is, &quot;/usr/share/doc/rhm-0.2&quot;. Therefore, I see that there is a requirement for a README in here too. And, $QPID_SAMPLE=$QPID_SRC_HOME/java/client/example/src/main should be the typical solution.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have attached the README required.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Regards,&lt;br/&gt;
Senaka&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
